  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/laptops/\" rel=\"tag\">膝上电脑</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/www.engadget.com/media/2013/06/dell-dsc03293.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div><br />\n几周前，Dell 发布了 XPS 11，这是款设计独特的超极本；它的 11.6 吋屏幕可以翻转，当屏幕翻转超过 180 度之后会自动禁用按键。可惜这款笔记本电脑的具体发售时间没有公布，价格也还是个谜。我们这次有幸在 Computex 上目睹了它的风采，大家可以点进来看看我们动手玩之后的一些心得。<br />\n<br />\n<div class=\"postgallery\"><p><strong>Gallery: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/dell-xps-11/\">Dell XPS 11 動手玩</a></strong></p><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/dell-xps-11/5929700/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/06/dell-xps-11-2013-06-03-0_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/dell-xps-11/5929701/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/06/dell-xps-11-2013-06-03-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/dell-xps-11/5929702/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/06/dell-xps-11-2013-06-03-2_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/dell-xps-11/5929703/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/06/dell-xps-11-2013-06-03-3_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/dell-xps-11/5929704/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/06/dell-xps-11-2013-06-03-4_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a></div></div><p><br /><p class=\"continueReading\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/06/03/dell-xps-11-hands-on/\" rel=\"bookmark\">继续阅读全文 <em>Dell XPS 11 动手玩，Dell 对 Lenovo Yoga 做出的回答（视频）</em></a></p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/06/03/dell-xps-11-hands-on/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"ht